OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSoldier who shot boy can be
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fprosecuted, says court     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The family of a teenage boy shot dead  
OL,6, in Londonderry in 1972 have            
OL,7, successfully challenged a decision not 
OL,8, to prosecute the soldier who killed    
OL,9, him.                                   
OL,11,FDaniel Hegarty was 15 when he was shot 
OL,12,Ftwice in the head by a soldier.        
OL,14,FIn July 2021 the Public Prosecution    
OL,15,FService (PPS) announced it was dropping
OL,16,Fthe prosecution of the veteran known as
OL,17,FSoldier B.                             
OL,19,FThe Court of Appeal has now quashed    
OL,20,Fthat decision.                         
